</script></div><div data-rid="7dc169a0-0eac-4f87-b541-7545d1c4017b" class="r-1o8qfha"><div data-rid="c964886b-f63e-470b-8807-0600670464b3" class="r-ybkqlm"><div data-rid="0211497a-32d7-489d-b61f-4626a3e42da7" class="r-1amzq70"><div data-rid="98a35810-a8a8-47f3-9759-90db19386184" class="r-9tk30s alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Respiratory Health</span></div></div><div data-rid="a31f9165-6b23-4f64-9dcb-3433c2214447" class="r-y3bnyw"><div data-rid="2f9e2c18-bce0-4b7a-9c86-8adc334546fb" class="r-1f1e5ui alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Ex-Smokers, A Pharmacist Ranked the 5<br>Best Things for Your Lungs</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="891399d9-30a5-4297-867c-3cfe32167f4b" class="r-1r6ipvd"><div data-rid="489d7ba6-20cb-4de2-8207-bc5a4c42e25b" class="r-fo695s alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">He lost his grandmother and two aunts to<br>smoking. Now he's ranking every lung<br>recovery method — from free daily habits to<br>the clinically studied formula he built himself.</span></div></div><div data-rid="b2f5e5e6-e2e1-4906-848a-3c64a3250c82" class="r-1p4612o"><div data-rid="131bb15c-d85a-4bc7-8214-d2acf7391b69" class="r-67smvs"><div data-rid="727e218b-36c6-43ae-8daa-a85848fba790" class="r-6k22z2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>By Margaret Ellison, Health Editor</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="12523b5e-8aac-4f99-93d5-07982148b043" class="r-1p03uw8"><div data-rid="d1326614-5322-4996-836b-3f9536deb9db" class="r-18qgvyt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">·</span></div></div><div data-rid="501505a4-e56d-43fd-8481-92b4c9c0baac" class="r-hdclas alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>8 min read</p></span></div><div data-rid="12602534-c314-4c0d-9b63-2cf148483f84" class="r-1n8gzs7"><div data-rid="5c0e5888-dc81-452e-8a6e-358b7ab454d2" class="r-1rklbly alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">·</span></div></div><div data-rid="94e63dab-b2aa-4cbe-9d63-e19fc34a1381" class="r-1y92nz1"><div data-rid="6262aac3-da5d-4ecb-ae11-ca301413ae52" class="r-zll3mz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Updated Feb 2026</p></span></div></div></div><picture data-rid="dcc1e497-6c20-43d5-a1c2-0040b98b5c1f" class="r-kkp6dr"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/2ba3ea30-df5e-421e-862f-d1543cd5bea7?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/2ba3ea30-df5e-421e-862f-d1543cd5bea7?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/2ba3ea30-df5e-421e-862f-d1543cd5bea7?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/2ba3ea30-df5e-421e-862f-d1543cd5bea7" class="r-188bfeb" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="f8f83851-acac-4ad5-b0f1-29bfd7c12b34" class="r-ttf8m6"><div data-rid="86044330-2495-49c4-8357-ab935d5ad96d" class="r-ut9ma3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">You quit smoking. That was the hard part.</span></div></div><div data-rid="0387080d-bd1d-435f-bdc1-0c9400fcca2e" class="r-19bzg8c"><div data-rid="e63ae865-de67-4b7a-8da9-33976498cc02" class="r-1y1wds7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">But you still cough every morning. You still get<br>winded on the stairs. There's still that heavy, tight<br>feeling in your chest — like you're breathing<br>through a wet towel.</span></div></div><div data-rid="919dd87f-7324-4f1b-baf2-3edaa1186a37" class="r-lbty6z"><div data-rid="7b3869ca-8fe2-49c9-a3e8-37ac9acf0466" class="r-1rjgd3j alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>That's because quitting stops the damage. It<br>doesn't undo it. Years of tar, mucus, and<br>inflammation don't disappear on their own.&nbsp;<strong>Your lungs need help finishing the job.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="fc1e602c-665b-4e9d-a0fa-457ac26bb792" class="r-1rge8ib"><div data-rid="62d8055c-9aa7-45e6-bc98-79b68993fd26" class="r-1xwkscz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Here are the 5 best ways to give them that help —<br>ranked from good to best.</span></div></div><div data-rid="add10dfd-a282-4944-bf9a-318a7367787b" class="r-1n7o70i"><div data-rid="9f843d35-9cac-460f-8741-a50999718f0a" class="r-1fbzm88"><div data-rid="0524d2f9-7842-40cc-a264-a36e749d41bb" class="r-1uxb0tn"><div data-rid="ac589da7-9d3f-4a34-b75b-af271b6ca750" class="r-1xo29bf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">5</span></div></div><div data-rid="bd503846-2be5-4bc2-89da-61ed44ad94e5" class="r-yysrvj"><div data-rid="5bd35d69-7253-413f-8ed2-57ab656f4f6d" class="r-1wqudkj"><div data-rid="84eb8734-61b5-4c46-abc1-028897084a32" class="r-1y6yqjt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Steam Therapy & Hydration</span></div></div><div data-rid="79a85b54-1fa2-411a-94a1-7bc6f14e0f40" class="r-1u9a2eh"><div data-rid="fbb3e692-64d6-4555-87ce-35dda36336d9" class="r-1v11570 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Free · Instant relief · No equipment</span></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="a4e86625-b7ae-4504-9fd2-dbfd7af1d407" class="r-1c1f2o3"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/b298c9b8-c35c-492b-a79e-41e5bf6554d4?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/b298c9b8-c35c-492b-a79e-41e5bf6554d4?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/b298c9b8-c35c-492b-a79e-41e5bf6554d4?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/b298c9b8-c35c-492b-a79e-41e5bf6554d4" class="r-1acoqh6" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="0383b660-c485-4164-9369-08a0a15fa5dc" class="r-1kkl7ao"><div data-rid="d91eb5a7-e78e-45c1-a187-6493dacb5ac4" class="r-1b6xijk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Think of steam as a hot shower for the inside of<br>your lungs.</span></div></div><div data-rid="b1eef6ae-0d6d-4a9e-be8f-7fa8eece10b6" class="r-5mma9b"><div data-rid="80d54551-f11f-4b55-84d5-f7facc3d2779" class="r-1ubq8br alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Smoking coated your airways with thick, sticky<br>mucus. Now that you've quit, your body is trying<br>to clear it out — but it needs help loosening the<br>gunk.&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26)"><strong>Warm, moist air softens that mucus so you can finally cough it up.</strong></span></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="e26be795-08fa-41aa-9606-3a9e4ca24195" class="r-1xy4pfy"><div data-rid="1d700a2a-4090-4fa8-a31f-687d3e2c900f" class="r-1bmhptl alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">One study found that steam improved mucus<br>clearance significantly in people with chronic<br>lung issues.</span></div></div><div data-rid="e1402800-f118-46c2-a1bc-d834c43b342b" class="r-ysg5zr"><div data-rid="6a10da39-18da-4ea2-9d51-a5b6cc144f52" class="r-fp9cc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">How to do it:</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> Hot water in a bowl. Towel over<br>your head. Breathe deeply for 5-10 minutes. Do it<br>2-3 times a day. Drink 8+ glasses of water to thin<br>mucus from the inside out.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="fcb8fc6e-58f6-4180-b7c6-4419f5b96216" class="r-d3lps5"><div data-rid="4cc9167f-6d3b-4089-9874-f21c05500fa9" class="r-52pokg"><div data-rid="c26d4f49-2a67-42ec-960d-46aa5c43d520" class="r-xkig6p alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Quick Take</span></div></div><div data-rid="4c862a04-2608-495b-a288-b97c5fbcef21" class="r-tyvbte"><div data-rid="021ba601-ab1b-4aaa-bd5a-c22fc8a58896" class="r-17znbh"><div data-rid="b9ed530d-9916-4f68-b94d-dd78cdc9cc5d" class="r-1o48ikj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">You'll feel a difference the very first time</span></div><div data-rid="bdb0fc1f-b86a-4a76-9416-cce35da548aa" class="r-3euxnk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="e24b7fe4-5bda-41a9-8117-6d986a9ca5ae" class="r-1qunini"><div data-rid="993ec281-c7d0-427d-9c7c-5bd746e8262e" class="r-1a8i5dd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Costs nothing — just hot water and a<br>towel</span></div><div data-rid="ee966e06-5e07-4f60-af0c-4b4edf0a744b" class="r-6hf94r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="c336cdb3-7b9f-4593-bfc0-dfff317f2e1d" class="r-844u5g"><div data-rid="752043b7-df8b-4786-ab83-04bdffb9ce05" class="r-9rmfs1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Loosens mucus so your lungs can start<br>cleaning house</span></div><div data-rid="ed54377b-b600-40a8-b6a6-ec3736da91f8" class="r-yiqfuj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="b45c33b8-6635-4c99-ab2c-df24dca30626" class="r-orfxrk"><div data-rid="7f1dcb9f-026b-4e94-8a78-12d021a0a5e2" class="r-1emi4rq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">The catch:</span><span style="color: #6B6B6B; font-weight: 400"> Steam works on surface-level<br>mucus. It can't support the deeper cleanup<br>your lungs need after years of smoking. For<br>that, you need something that works from the<br>inside.</span></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="458d5a0e-e75e-4d0e-adc5-877815670f9d" class="r-umbz69"><div data-rid="e8ebb261-0536-4545-a7bb-39381d48f080" class="r-1vaq82p"><div data-rid="20fe9f48-a9f0-4e19-a523-909427fd7242" class="r-1skrld3"><div data-rid="ec82ddec-9038-4fab-ae60-820f932d2bdc" class="r-16lox4f alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">4</span></div></div><div data-rid="e789876e-3a0e-40f1-8bb8-704e93c71874" class="r-1xy2067"><div data-rid="27d4cf08-6122-4544-9271-1cd3e9b5a7c2" class="r-g07xhq"><div data-rid="63909a42-3586-4473-b3db-0820ab41ee3d" class="r-133jx4a alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Anti-Inflammatory Foods</span></div></div><div data-rid="7f8f4f06-b800-453c-a620-98f42e735dc7" class="r-1mamla5"><div data-rid="424bff00-053d-4276-aa2f-348f897e72f6" class="r-15xz1v8 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Free · Long-term benefits · Easy to start</span></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="525ef1ee-7088-4676-94c7-f6c7fc729905" class="r-1rt2k39"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/e17377c8-4d0f-48af-8db8-efe695d00385?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/e17377c8-4d0f-48af-8db8-efe695d00385?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/e17377c8-4d0f-48af-8db8-efe695d00385?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/e17377c8-4d0f-48af-8db8-efe695d00385" class="r-2qlqrb" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="06cf69bd-3d4c-4d0d-b75c-dc4fca77912a" class="r-tzflun"><div data-rid="6b4bcb67-9cf1-46d6-8cc7-ec49afb77722" class="r-1agjqrf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Smoking lit a fire inside your lungs. Even after<br>you quit, that inflammation keeps smoldering<br>like embers that won't go out.&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26)"><strong>Certain foods act </strong></span><strong>like a fire extinguisher.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="c765cad8-7717-4c05-9a71-49a37c002e90" class="r-hanxqk"><div data-rid="6d2ddf2d-e4ec-45cc-929f-0868f3ddb9a7" class="r-u95nar alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Blueberries</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> — slowed lung function decline by<br>up to 38% in people who ate 2+ servings a week.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="b91452f3-a52d-4673-93e9-737263982e81" class="r-1ojuq6w"><div data-rid="c57ad3df-e615-43a4-b035-f887252d49c1" class="r-p3jy5v alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Apples</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> — 5 a week is linked to stronger lungs in<br>ex-smokers.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="7f029d61-d563-4e23-9bf4-4a6e04498aed" class="r-1av3i4n"><div data-rid="3d70cd9f-582e-4e36-ab6e-aa27781f6188" class="r-1039hmu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Turmeric</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> — smokers with high curcumin intake<br>had nearly 10% better lung function.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="b0f071c2-9007-457a-9df1-665893cb21b8" class="r-jdhocd"><div data-rid="727e9697-4adb-4a49-8a71-d9defc22c397" class="r-hmhdpj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Green tea</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> — contains a compound that may help<br>protect lung tissue from scarring.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="7a46e2a9-906a-45ff-bd8d-d19625773915" class="r-1hhn81j"><div data-rid="89acb513-5e4b-4142-839b-b9bc2fb6a98b" class="r-1vl3ae6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Add these to meals you're already eating. It's<br>easier than you think.</span></div></div><div data-rid="43322c65-acb1-4a93-83a6-e4ae2bbb5601" class="r-1abssov"><div data-rid="060f9e70-1f45-4843-8fb5-c5e36362698e" class="r-1sdjl53"><div data-rid="426b32d1-6868-47ff-8631-5800cfef38f9" class="r-9pzst3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Quick Take</span></div></div><div data-rid="c386420a-0194-47be-bbc1-6c71fd19ee56" class="r-19d7zro"><div data-rid="6013ba71-bc8a-4765-b882-47ddfc51422e" class="r-1287obd"><div data-rid="59d1d35a-f347-4d4c-927d-29b42239e585" class="r-1d9asc0 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Fights the hidden inflammation smoking<br>left behind</span></div><div data-rid="f3642e0c-8c1d-44bd-82fc-c65f92aeac64" class="r-8hx9ie alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="aafcd8ca-a830-4234-a137-93f29008fdcc" class="r-19ocotl"><div data-rid="049d1de7-1c2d-4551-9363-6389a5785328" class="r-bz6hsq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Add to meals you're already eating</span></div><div data-rid="29df0c05-b219-4e92-922b-b161eb489b20" class="r-luxfzi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="d182ada1-e4f9-4cc0-9db9-7e20f28cc05d" class="r-i44ydm"><div data-rid="d0c2a0e9-3489-4c1a-8ad8-46bf7d705c96" class="r-z8yb6r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Benefits your whole body, not just your<br>lungs</span></div><div data-rid="40594657-64fa-47fd-b036-e53b678b296c" class="r-sqy2ub alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="eacfb924-3354-48b4-bfc7-fc724387a6a9" class="r-1im67if"><div data-rid="90430108-52d9-4395-8ad9-bf971e77ac20" class="r-z22pkr alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26)"><strong>The catch:</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(107, 107, 107)"> Diet takes months to show real<br>results. And let's be honest — most people<br>don't eat 5 apples a week. This is a solid long- term play, not a fast fix.</span></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="7459b4e3-3114-4853-8312-3ed6912f8da2" class="r-1hffxy0"><div data-rid="0ded069a-0330-4ca2-b942-7ea2d718dbcd" class="r-qu8xrr"><div data-rid="4e52fc27-e3ad-4e64-908d-24439669dfa7" class="r-b74xd2"><div data-rid="493f68e6-0f78-4123-94dd-37ab04bf3957" class="r-ciwp8b alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">3</span></div></div><div data-rid="f995ff1d-567b-44e3-8042-6172604531ec" class="r-1vn53yq"><div data-rid="03c886bd-4420-4133-b2ef-5c18af7466d8" class="r-1q6zknt"><div data-rid="2f1d0c98-4add-4849-971d-5a2684d78fc6" class="r-1wpuf0e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Daily Breathing Exercises</span></div></div><div data-rid="b6ebc91c-1947-46f2-9321-2ec9017f4f7c" class="r-13rosg8"><div data-rid="a3f44881-1f96-4c8c-a21f-43eaaac6d2e3" class="r-to0eow alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Free · 5 minutes a day · Results in 2 weeks</span></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="c408e6fe-9406-4aa1-8d5f-ece38192a752" class="r-1lntqgh"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/fbad8dd7-1321-45a4-ade3-b35b046130b1?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/fbad8dd7-1321-45a4-ade3-b35b046130b1?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/fbad8dd7-1321-45a4-ade3-b35b046130b1?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/fbad8dd7-1321-45a4-ade3-b35b046130b1" class="r-1qwuk51" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="1742917e-54bc-4cb1-85af-6b2d7728e5d2" class="r-1q1kadt"><div data-rid="cfe38926-2727-4287-bb0e-c56c16a5cc05" class="r-aztpt2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Sounds too simple. But the science is strong.</span></div></div><div data-rid="2402258d-5cb7-4e3c-bd4b-7dbdbc08942b" class="r-grnoq7"><div data-rid="81d366cf-91d5-4b9e-9aa9-31956f15b40c" class="r-10grzbb alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Smoking trained you to take short, shallow<br>breaths. Over time, your diaphragm — the big<br>muscle under your lungs — got weak.&nbsp;<strong>Breathing exercises wake it back up.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="b18cf9d1-179a-4f17-bad2-50119f2883dd" class="r-1snmipj"><div data-rid="98fc1918-c270-4523-b68b-1b1e31a1ba26" class="r-7x7u7d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">One study: after just </span></div><div data-rid="49decdc2-636f-4f63-ab23-169aa0a34d19" class="r-8t9yow"><div data-rid="111be98c-7bd1-461a-a98d-fb40aea8c2a9" class="r-yu07uu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">2 weeks of daily deep</span></div><div data-rid="82ef7f12-2b19-46c7-adf1-e835303509f8" class="r-12bb030 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">breathing</span></div></div><div data-rid="e219b389-8f6a-4bd7-beb6-17c6d00bf7cf" class="r-1yuhn20 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">, smokers showed real improvements</span></div><div data-rid="2357b53e-ef12-45ca-bcaa-5f101134fdda" class="r-16ov3cz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">in lung capacity.</span></div></div><div data-rid="f15d9517-d907-488d-b6d8-46dd8baf0b94" class="r-1hnpd4c"><div data-rid="6408c406-24d3-42e6-9c98-5d5918dac9b4" class="r-17r7m96 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Another found that 4 weeks of diaphragmatic<br>breathing led to noticeable gains in breathing<br>power.</span></div></div><div data-rid="0c3b1918-818e-437a-94fc-62371ed9a020" class="r-7qsla7"><div data-rid="c269063e-cd51-4e3b-80a1-b4790d3da1fe" class="r-hakdyx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Start here:</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> Breathe in through your nose for 2<br>counts. Out through pursed lips (like blowing out<br>a candle) for 4 counts. That's it. This is the<br>foundation of every pulmonary rehab program in<br>the country.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="a1db9a56-8a87-4391-a8bc-15cc2521d55e" class="r-t5l9si"><div data-rid="e3c48289-c863-4032-9fad-f03c6f4e2a02" class="r-1up8og0"><div data-rid="7c18eb7a-ae3a-461c-a4e1-9635efb6d790" class="r-agcn08 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">2 weeks</span></div></div><div data-rid="77fa5a4e-d2bc-4269-bd41-fc98e7624882" class="r-1wifd38"><div data-rid="27b9bc54-bf01-458e-81d9-9e80b4f0c100" class="r-7ho9tt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">to measurable lung improvement from daily<br>breathing exercises</span></div></div></div><div data-rid="e9f62c1f-2792-4f1e-81a4-c881c274d073" class="r-1je94dn"><div data-rid="15f928b0-6550-48d1-b534-4688f8dca6c9" class="r-iu6jqb"><div data-rid="656b61c3-da60-40c4-b179-ceea3c4fcb8a" class="r-134264w alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Quick Take</span></div></div><div data-rid="9b0acad3-4857-4071-9a98-124bb5d7a5ce" class="r-1561at6"><div data-rid="b7f7fd60-3cdd-463f-9e09-84f5bf526bc9" class="r-17lqebh"><div data-rid="7985573b-663a-440d-8634-e3a64cfd7fff" class="r-1qhfi9s alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Fastest free method — results in days, not<br>months</span></div><div data-rid="cc7d4fcd-fe74-4d8f-8a1e-1f355ac41551" class="r-13akucq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="e656f6f3-2654-4feb-ab97-9a37282b853a" class="r-6k7ie1"><div data-rid="ba40d187-e03e-4e62-85e2-f11b57863608" class="r-zqmey4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Do it in bed, in a chair, or in your car</span></div><div data-rid="6b5b54f9-ce09-4827-8a0d-708414a7f4c9" class="r-kwf6a alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="b6823e07-1b5e-48e7-b053-cae0e77d001c" class="r-1n5t5i5"><div data-rid="376f8536-7042-4efe-bdd5-d7689cb0f667" class="r-1o4fvsf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Recommended by the American Lung<br>Association</span></div><div data-rid="b1f6c6db-2006-4058-8f51-9c7c77348853" class="r-na4r9y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="89056f24-23cd-4e8f-a6cc-0074458b4a8a" class="r-mu99co"><div data-rid="48c504cd-9ef1-45ae-a707-df7ba380a2e9" class="r-hvwoap alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26)"><strong>The catch:</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(107, 107, 107)"> Breathing exercises strengthen the<br>muscles around your lungs. They don't help<br>clear the buildup clogging your airways. You're building a stronger engine — but the exhaust pipe is still blocked.</span></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="656c4352-6fe6-43c8-a340-f1d9f88f71b8" class="r-k56s7h"><div data-rid="a4b2ff06-8f1d-457c-8801-332aff34fe98" tabindex="0" role="link" class="r-1nckxte"><div data-rid="ba3df14d-aa17-4f86-b5fc-e27111d8ea4b" class="r-1ipya4t alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Want to skip to our top pick? </span></div><div data-rid="38076069-982e-44a0-a65c-1c2c0e315322" class="r-axtvyr"><div data-rid="05b13ad7-d080-4d47-807b-615d5e5d7173" tabindex="0" role="link" class="r-2rto59 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>See why</p></span></div><div data-rid="efa2fb2c-97b8-40ca-9587-f57a6dc115fd" tabindex="0" role="link" class="r-1lc7y6x alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>BetterLungs® took the #1 spot →</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="3e915cab-0173-45c5-8163-5a28d6c1ef6d" class="r-dllxx4"><div data-rid="c33ee5b0-7608-47b5-b25c-1830e879f007" class="r-hewqnu"><div data-rid="27b900e5-d5ab-4f87-916b-606696e1a1cc" class="r-1wt2zbf"><div data-rid="ab215d25-1abf-473a-8fdb-ecdbdddfed7c" class="r-1lkpz61 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">2</span></div></div><div data-rid="8765c839-6148-4205-b33c-b49ba83aa3aa" class="r-17kuqsf"><div data-rid="0c63c95f-7441-4857-8194-9490e5344835" class="r-1s3jhyf"><div data-rid="400d6c59-36b9-4cd2-810d-fad2d1f65f97" class="r-vm94fx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Regular Cardio Exercise</span></div></div><div data-rid="47154209-e2d5-461a-b000-9a59a2bd5cc8" class="r-1fjek03"><div data-rid="30869c60-4c25-4243-a3dc-cd50970a159f" class="r-193yodt alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Free · 20-30 min/day · Doctor-recommended</span></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="495b5302-e6a7-48f4-b31c-f78add5a8672" class="r-10kpsax"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/795646fe-9e5d-424d-a581-050a6a2d67a4?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/795646fe-9e5d-424d-a581-050a6a2d67a4?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/795646fe-9e5d-424d-a581-050a6a2d67a4?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/795646fe-9e5d-424d-a581-050a6a2d67a4" class="r-14rnjcg" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="c242f9b9-635d-4232-a4a6-5c8d2d234d58" class="r-3p4483"><div data-rid="b2373081-fb97-429f-93fa-33c1145bd585" class="r-107wevq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Every lung doctor agrees on this one:&nbsp;<strong>move your body.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="38701ca3-ddb3-4970-9706-c5dbe4a163cc" class="r-15m436t"><div data-rid="04626fd2-de9d-4c16-b994-8dc11858fddb" class="r-vzcjuq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Here's the wild part —&nbsp;<strong>ex-smokers benefit MORE from exercise than people who never smoked.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="d7d44514-ab45-4821-9e83-81c72e882e2e" class="r-34k1hb"><div data-rid="c6f52dc5-e0b1-49c2-b1e7-375846fd534a" class="r-cugkz2 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">One study found that a 12-week walking program<br>improved lung capacity in former smokers at a<br>higher rate than non-smokers. Your lungs are<br>waiting for the signal to rebuild.</span></div></div><div data-rid="83419e76-d83f-4a65-863c-3073132299e0" class="r-1sob5pt"><div data-rid="8f992f53-06bd-4e6a-b411-9739d2da9344" class="r-ouhpa1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Think of it like cleaning a dusty attic. The harder<br>you breathe, the more air pushes through your<br>lungs, helping your body sweep out old debris.</span></div></div><div data-rid="509100a9-cc58-4f77-b1f6-c4cb3b855c1f" class="r-orbdf5"><div data-rid="eb284b12-c702-4690-b09b-12da4f2cb2c9" class="r-1u5ljj3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Start with 15-minute walks.</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> Build to 30 minutes<br>most days.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="d96f6315-2c58-4cc1-b8f4-1c76f28dfe42" class="r-21lul3"><div data-rid="43332b16-d4fb-4dcd-b43a-1d6c806fb230" class="r-19a2jdn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Swimming is especially good — it forces<br>controlled breathing. One study found that<br>quitting combined with exercise&nbsp;<strong>improved lung </strong></p><p><strong>function by 15% in under 8 weeks.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="8452889f-b826-41c6-8271-e649bee49a08" class="r-fkslkb"><div data-rid="f52dbef5-eeab-4914-8a75-1745dfce31d0" class="r-mnmqfu"><div data-rid="4385e6b5-647b-436b-9716-9b24e0584cc6" class="r-my9o5o alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Up to 30%</span></div></div><div data-rid="9c4f51a6-8134-4b13-9fa2-3275b97bc79b" class="r-1ql9j5t"><div data-rid="6da81b7e-caad-49a0-8cb3-5128dfb88fdf" class="r-1fp5uzm alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">potential lung function gain within 2-12 weeks<br>of quitting + exercise</span></div></div></div><div data-rid="6ce3571e-13f3-4f19-bb44-c8b821f575ec" class="r-f3j2j4"><div data-rid="e13f43b5-3b95-4393-9589-27ffe91200aa" class="r-tr0sj4"><div data-rid="de53c7b2-e575-411c-9096-09a8b6797004" class="r-1ikfk2f alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Quick Take</span></div></div><div data-rid="3427550c-b85a-4049-82e3-7a4a166bee00" class="r-hfniws"><div data-rid="61c71836-9480-4b07-8f5c-68d69724d460" class="r-t6eb7i"><div data-rid="1bfcd6f8-71e2-4de1-8b34-95be49b767d0" class="r-j7asb7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Most evidence-backed method for lung<br>recovery</span></div><div data-rid="dde863ab-61f2-457b-b7d1-d61515c6467e" class="r-18iqmgw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="8cc52242-8e40-48ff-b841-2f9c97909711" class="r-o9897c"><div data-rid="7d836580-c3d7-4f38-9b5e-7d5ab1c69852" class="r-18ggpcw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Helps your heart, mood, and energy too</span></div><div data-rid="bb7ef25e-736f-4bc6-83fa-e2210331aaba" class="r-1hsyzsx alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div><div data-rid="28160a98-b069-43ad-bd30-907363acdf96" class="r-tzd93h"><div data-rid="20f5bc1c-e8f0-4e3b-812b-5fd2fc6d8073" class="r-tv42ld alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Ex-smokers see bigger gains than non-<br>smokers</span></div><div data-rid="5e57dfec-2664-4ad3-ae4f-47599ce37013" class="r-xu2f7s alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">✓</span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="c4cfb0b0-4d5d-4c4f-ae71-0c03ba1419cd" class="r-19f0nkk"><div data-rid="9bca6d4d-57b8-4a9c-b47b-c84b90ed2171" class="r-mu23rz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(26, 26, 26)"><strong>The catch:</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(107, 107, 107)"> Exercise takes weeks to months. And if you can barely walk to the mailbox without wheezing, "just exercise more" isn't helpful advice. It's frustrating. Your lungs need support they can use right now — even on the days you can't get off the couch.</span></p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="42553929-dc23-4fde-8500-c258e9983d1f" class="r-7y0dez"><div data-rid="d367004d-1c92-463a-8795-03e0a2c5d845" class="r-nboqf8 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">· · ·</span></div></div><div data-rid="88dd970e-adce-4d0a-97d7-6089e293057c" class="r-ww85c"><div data-rid="b020d52e-f5bf-4893-a045-23ed26edf57b" class="r-17dbye1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Here's the truth about everything above.</span></div></div><div data-rid="fb5ea0c7-6921-4498-8c70-3b38cfa6a64a" class="r-1r4af06"><div data-rid="1a2507a6-a6e2-4721-9856-85eef086e65d" class="r-gb25b3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Steam, food, breathing drills, exercise —&nbsp;<strong>they all work ON your lungs. But none of them work</strong><br><strong>INSIDE your lungs.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="c0af4e7a-1273-4b0c-9fcf-d11aa2d5f514" class="r-lupcjq"><div data-rid="e2143bc4-cbfe-4b06-a709-406498fd927f" class="r-vss9jr alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">None of them support your body's ability to clear<br>the deep, stuck-on buildup that's been sitting in<br>your airways since your first cigarette.</span></div></div><div data-rid="7b6a7074-d598-4cd2-ae6f-c307b541f067" class="r-1203dhz"><div data-rid="ae373827-cc43-403b-bc52-ffb59a0993af" class="r-1gvlihk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">The stuff that makes you cough every morning.<br>The stuff that makes breathing feel like sucking<br>air through a coffee straw.</span></div></div><div data-rid="077d5a63-d6e5-4d26-8e81-d66be058d65a" class="r-dogi6t"><div data-rid="02635e04-e65b-49dd-b419-aab4f380540a" class="r-hl1kou alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">For that, you need something different.</span></div></div><div data-rid="fe227bb2-de27-4cdd-9fe5-08cb84ce41db" data-alchemy-url-hashmark="final-item" tabindex="-1" id="final-item" data-alchemy-url-hashmark-ignore="true" class="r-1j8jjc7"><div data-rid="c5295e76-4639-4309-9073-188848df797f" class="r-kiu8tu"><div data-rid="9d2e2d8d-0ccf-49a9-99c9-42f822cb72ad" class="r-1jn3s1b"><div data-rid="ee09f52c-48cf-4910-b9b5-b94d02804179" class="r-14nrgw9 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Editor's Pick</p></span></div></div></div><div data-rid="0636a869-e47b-4fce-bb95-892116784dbc" class="r-1sxjq0a"><div data-rid="674c9b89-64a2-4332-a2cf-f41f5f685319" class="r-s0mqd9"><div data-rid="a5512230-6107-4873-a4ca-b2d8c407d82f" class="r-s84ud4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">1</span></div></div><div data-rid="bf841df4-ed85-4c08-aa9c-72a8fd802a37" class="r-iajsjj"><div data-rid="b90b6833-15a4-4ced-869b-06a5a02166a9" class="r-156qhab"><div data-rid="a3b05db4-9c9a-43b5-a65d-14f920c69fcf" class="r-1yrrb2r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">BetterLungs® Mullein &<br>Chlorophyll Drops</span></div></div><div data-rid="3092dc19-b8e6-47b4-8256-b0029499dc31" class="r-1t3uvgs"><div data-rid="b84db23e-a65f-4a4e-a4fc-7a068dedfda7" class="r-1rxtw9p alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Clinically studied · 1.4 million+ customers ·<br>365-day guarantee</span></div></div></div></div><picture data-rid="8cb49b03-a42a-4421-bcd9-ecf5ede0d31e" tabindex="0" role="link" class="r-iq6ydi"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ad0cf6bf-6c7c-4455-a429-e49bf1cd5ce1?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ad0cf6bf-6c7c-4455-a429-e49bf1cd5ce1?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ad0cf6bf-6c7c-4455-a429-e49bf1cd5ce1?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/ad0cf6bf-6c7c-4455-a429-e49bf1cd5ce1" class="r-18w7ig3" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="a25a4287-727d-4c33-993c-66a64c8554c2" class="r-17ngcid"><div data-rid="1e56a5b6-26f4-4f8d-b232-f1076e8b1ebc" class="r-ubvc4l alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Before we get into the formula, you need to know<br>why it exists.</span></div></div><div data-rid="b0b156a9-c767-454a-8025-134ab293992b" class="r-1sgr2at"><div data-rid="82e143be-b674-4cc7-81a7-05fe0a9f4429" class="r-1ak4d0e alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">His grandmother — everyone called her<br>"Shuggie" — had smoked for most of her life. By<br>the time the damage caught up with her, the<br>doctors could only manage symptoms. She<br>couldn't breathe. She couldn't walk across the<br>room. And Chris, a trained medic, couldn't save<br>her.</span></div></div><div data-rid="5637d343-0edc-4388-977a-bb3464f36e3c" class="r-fofb23"><div data-rid="957f932b-60d2-4be0-88c2-08769102f8e4" class="r-1g3xi1o alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Then he lost two aunts the same way. Same<br>cause. Smoking-related lung complications.</span></div></div><div data-rid="0a15e195-b0c7-452b-a275-a72c2288463b" class="r-16rgytj"><div data-rid="7542088f-fc07-4d60-8a5a-5bb9e95ccf90" class="r-ky3ytd alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">After leaving the Army, Chris earned his PharmD<br>from the University of Texas at Austin. He studied<br>every drug, every treatment, every option on the<br>market.</span></div></div><div data-rid="cc037747-8a28-47ff-b04a-4fbe4fd75131" class="r-a7ej7h"><div data-rid="796763c7-64b6-4d59-a6d9-e42bf50e0fd7" class="r-19gcm7d alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">He kept hitting the same wall — the prescription<br>medications managed symptoms, but they<br>didn't support the body's natural ability to<br>recover.</span></div></div><div data-rid="93964b3e-b901-42de-902f-176f78be7f05" class="r-oxkvfa"><div data-rid="984736ad-703d-42b4-b751-a944a21ce3f4" class="r-1fk07pc alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">So he built something himself.</span></div></div><picture data-rid="9782e990-1ca8-459e-831c-a97567e0b851" class="r-1iz2757"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d59dd7e1-13b1-4842-bebd-2476c3fc4eb4?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d59dd7e1-13b1-4842-bebd-2476c3fc4eb4?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d59dd7e1-13b1-4842-bebd-2476c3fc4eb4?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/d59dd7e1-13b1-4842-bebd-2476c3fc4eb4" class="r-1y7zrs7" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="f0bd04b8-3a77-418f-b21e-75382e3603c2" class="r-1x2uerk"><div data-rid="8af296e7-3fac-406f-853a-c5a3712db369" class="r-167wgfy alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">BetterLungs® uses just two ingredients.</span></div></div><div data-rid="ed545f02-a39a-43af-ab43-5d03fae813e4" class="r-kv83h3"><div data-rid="b66e1984-40a8-45f3-be73-89df936525cf" class="r-cyu8cj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Mullein leaf extract</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> — a plant used for breathing<br>problems for over 2,000 years.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="f3ada66c-38ff-4ec5-a4e2-ad67751cb7fc" class="r-1bxxgvh"><div data-rid="80701b2e-c5fc-495a-9e39-ba2eba66e90b" class="r-1tz53a5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Think of it like WD-40 for rusted pipes. It soothes<br>irritated airways with a soft, protective coating,<br>while its natural compounds help support your<br>body's ability to loosen and move out built-up<br>mucus.</span></div></div><div data-rid="f163a6d2-ceb2-4bbd-aab8-a95a18f0d7f3" class="r-6iy0ft"><div data-rid="2055a50f-77b4-4f22-b56b-13247f985ab6" class="r-51x7uf alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>One dropper delivers the equivalent of&nbsp;<strong>2,800mg of raw mullein leaf.</strong></p></span></div></div><div data-rid="ec2745f8-038a-4734-b82a-7b4ccc948c52" class="r-ly5hoz"><div data-rid="06da9ff5-cac4-46c6-89a6-4dee7e942b8f" class="r-1ef7h3f alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><span style="color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 600">Chlorophyll</span><span style="color: #4A4A4A; font-weight: 400"> — the green pigment from plants. It<br>provides antioxidant support that may help your<br>body manage the oxidative stress from years of<br>smoke exposure.</span></span></div></div><div data-rid="efc9f1ec-9692-423d-917a-52d4398a185f" class="r-b6j390"><div data-rid="a61a0ddf-0f40-412e-a34d-4f442c6238cf" class="r-1r5udxz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Think of it like sending a cleanup crew into your<br>system to deal with what smoking left behind.</span></div></div><picture data-rid="d8d74672-eb2a-4749-90de-6d1417aa43f6" class="r-1ka9vh0"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/74c67aed-6323-48bc-bf1a-7058174d8464?width=700" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/74c67aed-6323-48bc-bf1a-7058174d8464?width=700" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/74c67aed-6323-48bc-bf1a-7058174d8464?width=700" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/6bf67db6-09d6-4705-bab2-a1af9067f5a3/74c67aed-6323-48bc-bf1a-7058174d8464" class="r-es4vir" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="0e0af622-5801-47a1-8bdb-e58016b87b11" class="r-8yemup"><div data-rid="a0b74cd7-9566-415d-9a58-c54ec4f5275e" class="r-137r6w4 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Here's what separates BetterLungs® from every<br>other supplement on the shelf.</span></div></div><div data-rid="b594c350-dbe1-4186-8ee9-4c8b982381b1" class="r-kril1a"><div data-rid="1d526506-65a9-4c16-b890-561e1dad05b9" class="r-yhp49f alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">Most supplement companies don't test their<br>products at all.</span></div></div><div data-rid="cbee0ce2-d595-4965-a4f8-275fc84f0e36" class="r-s3htn8"><div data-rid="a12bb220-40a9-4560-9526-ca3352f1b6dc" class="r-1xpgdi7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">BetterLungs® did something different — they<br>hired an independent research lab to run a real<br>clinical study. 100 people. 60 days. Triple-blind.</span></div></div><div data-rid="e82006ad-b426-4d68-9adb-00f887e9296e" class="r-1kbg3ip"><div data-rid="77e1842c-2386-4188-954e-6a93130bd1e8" class="r-1lxsljk alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">That means </span></div><div data-rid="53d77cda-e241-4600-a830-b2b149877751" class="r-knwlju"><div data-rid="04bfe91c-300c-47a5-aedc-8039c7bbaf0b" class="r-17trflu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>nobody — not the participants, not</p></span></div><div data-rid="0f75f35f-9e20-402c-9886-7a543b1f7dce" class="r-kwr3c5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>the researchers, not the company — knew who<br>got the real drops and who got the placebo</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="f0cd4adb-30a7-4493-8985-71353dba8979" class="r-rtgz7a alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%">&nbsp;until</span></div><div data-rid="54059d1f-d43c-4b